summary: I am a Marketing Coordinator with nearly 6 years of Marketing experience. After working in the Food industry for 5 years in a strategic Marketing role and a Marketing Communication role I can proudly call myself an all-rounder. After this I made the change to the beauty industry. This industry already has gotten my interest since I was a little girl and I'm super happy to work in this field!
